[49m[38;5;9m- 25    [0m:[38;5;9m[49m **Amazon SNS and Amazon Pinpoint for active notifications.** When the urgency classifier flags an emergent voicemail, the notification path uses SNS for the basic mechanics (push to a topic, fan out to multiple subscribers including SMS, email, and push notifications) and optionally Pinpoint for richer mobile-app notifications and delivery tracking. The on-call clinician's pager or phone is a subscriber to the emergent topic.  
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     25[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Amazon SNS and Amazon Pinpoint for active notifications.** When the urgency classifier flags an emergent voicemail, the notification path uses SNS for the basic mechanics (push to a topic, fan out to multiple subscribers including SMS, email, and push notifications) and optionally Pinpoint for richer mobile-app notifications and delivery tracking. The on-call clinician's pager or phone is a subscriber to the emergent topic. The emergent SNS topic's resource policy pins the publish principal to the router Lambda's execution role ARN and pins subscription endpoints to the configured on-call rotation system endpoints, so neither arbitrary publishers nor unauthorized subscribers can interact with the topic.
